    "en": {
      "name": "Sky Striker Alternative - Lemnis Gate",
      "effect": "Target an equal number of \"Sky Striker Ace\" monsters and \"Sky Striker\" Spells in your GY; shuffle them into the Deck, then you can return to the hand up to 1 card on the field for every 3 cards shuffled. If a \"Sky Striker\" monster(s) is Special Summoned to your field while this card is in your GY (except during the Damage Step): You can banish this card; immediately after this effect resolves, Link Summon 1 \"Sky Striker Ace\" Link Monster. You can only use each effect of \"Sky Striker Alternative - Lemnis Gate\" once per turn.",
